<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="hearing-n">hearing <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'hɪərɪŋ/    美 /'hɪrɪŋ/  </p>
<p>[U]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>听力；听觉：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>lose one's hearing
失聪</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Listening to loud music at rock concerts has caused hearing loss in some teenagers.
在摇滚音乐会上听喧闹的音乐已使得一些青少年的听力受损。</p><footer>2010 湖南</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Please stay <strong>within hearing</strong>.
请保持在相互能听得到的范围内。</p></div></div>